2026-05-15T23:34:42.1128460Z 13    <!--
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1129039Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1129937Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1131194Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1132508Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1133507Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1134206Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1134776Z 20    -->
2026-05-15T23:34:42.1135534Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
