2026-05-15T23:34:42.2184436Z 250        <!--
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2185018Z 251            Same hardening for Glance's InvisibleActionTrampolineActivity.
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2186134Z 252            The library entry is singleInstance with its own taskAffinity
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2186948Z 253            but omits excludeFromRecents (unlike its sibling
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2187732Z 254            ActionTrampolineActivity which already has it). When the
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2188587Z 255            process dies before the trampoline finishes, the system can
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2189413Z 256            restore the task from Recents and replay onCreate with a
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2190791Z 257            stale Intent whose ACTION_INTENT extra is missing — which
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2191671Z 258            triggers an IllegalArgumentException ("List adapter activity
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2192564Z 259            trampoline invoked without specifying target intent"). Adding
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2193451Z 260            excludeFromRecents removes the Recents restoration vector,
2026-05-15T23:34:42.2194350Z 261            matching what Glance already does for ActionTrampolineActivity.
